Mira i Zoey w przerwach między koncertami na pełnych stadionach bronią fanów przed nadnaturalnymi zagrożeniami, korzystając ze swoich tajemnych mocy.","ageLongDescription":null,"releaseDate":null,"distributor":null,"distributorId":null,"genres":[{"id":"9212e3f5-252f-4d08-b375-2923037a4591","name":"animowany","description":""}],"trailers":["https://www.youtube.com/embed/loBwcgZt_m4"],"posters":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/KPopoweLowczynieplakat.jpg"],"pictures":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow8.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow7.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow6.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow5.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow4.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow3.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow2.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow1.jpg"],"posPosters":[],"banners":[],"ratings":[{"cinemaGroupId":null,"symbol":"10","value":"10","description":"od lat 10"}],"brightcoveVideos":[],"release":"2D/NAP","name":"K-popowe Łowczynie Demonów: Karaoke w Helios na Scenie","link":null,"screeningId":"9701c5c6-473b-4df6-9fa7-099c4bfe73ca","screenId":"bedc4eed-f0cb-48b8-95fe-c91f76b686bf","cinemaId":"d516a0dd-b0ab-4e15-85b2-0286eaf6dde6","timeFrom":"2026-06-11T16:30:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-11T18:16:00+02:00","saleTimeTo":"2026-06-11T17:00:00+02:00","reservationTimeTo":"2026-06-11T15:30:00+02:00","availabilityStatus":1,"maxOccupancy":145,"audience":0,"generalAdmission":false,"isScreenSwapping":false,"externalId":2868677,"items":[{"movieId":"4c6e0734-8000-45cf-9abe-161ae1a5ff6e","moviePrintId":"d882e05d-f8ef-4987-ba35-fb379d34fca7","timeFrom":"2026-06-11T16:30:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-11T18:16:00+02:00","movieName":"K-popowe Łowczynie Demonów: Karaoke","speakingType":"Napisy","printType":"2D","screenId":"bedc4eed-f0cb-48b8-95fe-c91f76b686bf","movieSubPrintLabel":"PS"}],"tagGroups":[{"symbol":"Projekty Specjalne","description":"","tags":[{"orderNo":6,"symbol":"HELIOS NA SCENIE","description":""}]}],"restrictedToCardTypeIds":[],"screenFeatures":[]},{"id":"8ede9a2d-3a2f-4ec2-9799-7ce8c9d2cbbf","duration":133,"description":"Jest rok 1939. Świat pogrąża się w chaosie. Tysiące wybitnych Polaków trafiają do rosyjskiej niewoli, gdzie poddawani są indoktrynacji będącej częścią wielkiego planu. Ambitny agent wroga stawia sobie za punkt honoru złamanie oporu jednego z nich. To młody pianista światowej sławy, cieszący się szacunkiem współosadzonych. Jego kapitulacja może skutkować przejściem wielu innych na stronę przeciwnika. Rozpoczyna się podstępna gra, pełna manipulacji, gróźb i obietnic. Każdy z więźniów zmuszony jest dokonać dramatycznego wyboru, z którym będzie musiał żyć lub umrzeć. Nieświadomi swojej roli, z utęsknieniem czekają na moment wyzwolenia, który może być ich zgubą. Towarzysze broni podejmą próbę śmiertelnie ryzykownej ucieczki czy zdadzą się na łaskę wroga? Czasu jest coraz mniej, bo swój ostateczny ruch może wykonać on w każdej chwili.","ageLongDescription":null,"releaseDate":null,"distributor":null,"distributorId":null,"genres":[{"id":"14c7bb44-6562-4ad9-8d7a-ab747fa73829","name":"dramat","description":""},{"id":"a78fead9-c0f8-4fc6-96de-c665a6458acd","name":"historyczny","description":""}],"trailers":[],"posters":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/pojedynekplakat.jpg"],"pictures":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/Pojedynek7(1).jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Pojedynek6(1).jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Pojedynek5(1).jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Pojedynek4(1).jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Pojedynek3(1).jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Pojedynek2(1).jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Pojedynek1(1).jpg"],"posPosters":[],"banners":[],"ratings":[{"cinemaGroupId":null,"symbol":"15","value":"15","description":"od lat 15"}],"brightcoveVideos":[],"release":"2D/NAP","name":"Pojedynek - KNT","link":null,"screeningId":"a0b495cf-1185-489c-afdc-a0f448e75159","screenId":"bedc4eed-f0cb-48b8-95fe-c91f76b686bf","cinemaId":"d516a0dd-b0ab-4e15-85b2-0286eaf6dde6","timeFrom":"2026-06-09T09:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-09T11:13:00+02:00","saleTimeTo":"2026-06-09T09:30:00+02:00","reservationTimeTo":"2026-06-09T08:00:00+02:00","availabilityStatus":1,"maxOccupancy":145,"audience":22,"generalAdmission":false,"isScreenSwapping":false,"externalId":7854117,"items":[{"movieId":"e09a334e-42f5-4b8b-82c6-ed98db9b0402","moviePrintId":"591e1922-e8ff-4fd6-81fe-64a352a206c1","timeFrom":"2026-06-09T09:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-09T11:13:00+02:00","movieName":"Pojedynek","speakingType":"Napisy","printType":"2D","screenId":"bedc4eed-f0cb-48b8-95fe-c91f76b686bf","movieSubPrintLabel":"PS"}],"tagGroups":[{"symbol":"Projekty Specjalne","description":"","tags":[{"orderNo":7,"symbol":"KINO NA TEMAT","description":""}]}],"restrictedToCardTypeIds":[],"screenFeatures":[]},{"id":"feee7612-9cd6-4397-a516-db46be76e2c4","duration":159,"description":"W 1939 roku Szpilman jest cenionym pianistą i kompozytorem, który mieszka wraz z rodziną w Warszawie. Kiedy do stolicy wkraczają naziści, życie żydowskiego muzyka zamienia się w koszmar: traci kolejne prawa, trafia do getta, obserwuje dwa powstania i próbuje przetrwać w zniszczonym mieście. Pomaga mu przypadek, łut szczęścia oraz miłość do muzyki.","ageLongDescription":null,"releaseDate":null,"distributor":null,"distributorId":null,"genres":[{"id":"b36e63dc-85ea-4670-93db-f785f49c720e","name":"biograficzny","description":""},{"id":"14c7bb44-6562-4ad9-8d7a-ab747fa73829","name":"dramat","description":""}],"trailers":["https://www.youtube.com/embed/KTDhBh_vL_Q"],"posters":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/pianistaplakat.png"],"pictures":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/Pianista7.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Pianista6.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Pianista5.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Pianista4.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Pianista3.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Pianista2.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Pianista1.jpg"],"posPosters":[],"banners":[],"ratings":[{"cinemaGroupId":null,"symbol":"15","value":"15","description":"od lat 15"}],"brightcoveVideos":[],"release":"2D/NAP","name":"Pianista w Helios RePlay","link":null,"screeningId":"39d79507-44ec-445c-b3d1-a97a81acacc1","screenId":"c2bfd325-cd71-48f8-a166-46ddae86d529","cinemaId":"d516a0dd-b0ab-4e15-85b2-0286eaf6dde6","timeFrom":"2026-06-14T15:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-14T17:39:00+02:00","saleTimeTo":"2026-06-14T15:30:00+02:00","reservationTimeTo":"2026-06-14T14:00:00+02:00","availabilityStatus":1,"maxOccupancy":164,"audience":4,"generalAdmission":false,"isScreenSwapping":false,"externalId":128645,"items":[{"movieId":"117e6eec-1144-4b1a-9600-a86530ca8b3a","moviePrintId":"98e18e82-1d60-4df6-ae6e-e9c76a4d486d","timeFrom":"2026-06-14T15:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-14T17:39:00+02:00","movieName":"Pianista","speakingType":"Napisy","printType":"2D","screenId":"c2bfd325-cd71-48f8-a166-46ddae86d529","movieSubPrintLabel":"ps"}],"tagGroups":[{"symbol":"Projekty Specjalne","description":"","tags":[{"orderNo":16,"symbol":"HELIOS REPLAY","description":""}]}],"restrictedToCardTypeIds":[],"screenFeatures":[]},{"id":"d7bb09f1-a1ea-4982-915d-db91d91397cc","duration":176,"description":"Nigdy nie jest za późno, by zacząć od nowa. Emanujący optymizmem i pogodą ducha portret dojrzałej kobiety, która robi wszystko, by ocalić swój dom i siebie.\n\n María Ángeles od 40 lat mieszka w słonecznym apartamencie w marokańskim Tangerze. Gdy zostaje zmuszona do jego opuszczenia, nie potrafi się z tym pogodzić. To, co początkowo wydaje się bolesną koniecznością, nieoczekiwanie staje się jednak nowym początkiem. W życiu Marii Ángeles pojawia się miejsce zarówno na nowych przyjaciół, jak i na niespodziewaną miłość. „Drugie życie” to zdobywca nagrody publiczności festiwalu w Wenecji. W roli głównej zachwycająca Carmen Maura, ikona filmów Almodóvara.","ageLongDescription":null,"releaseDate":null,"distributor":null,"distributorId":null,"genres":[{"id":"4a3d74ad-af64-4a6a-a640-e75c762899c8","name":"romans","description":""},{"id":"14c7bb44-6562-4ad9-8d7a-ab747fa73829","name":"dramat","description":""}],"trailers":["https://www.youtube.com/embed/8xyTxjwUwfQ"],"posters":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/drugiezycieplakat.jpg"],"pictures":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drugiezycie7.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drugiezycie6.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drugiezycie5.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drugiezycie4.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drugiezycie3.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drugiezycie2.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drugiezycie1.jpg"],"posPosters":[],"banners":[],"ratings":[{"cinemaGroupId":null,"symbol":"15","value":"15","description":"od lat 15"}],"brightcoveVideos":[],"release":"2D/NAP","name":"Drugie życie - Kino Kobiet","link":null,"screeningId":"906a5f19-dd96-40f4-b8dc-46619e82445b","screenId":"6f42a3dc-bbd0-4b84-897a-3d9badde17ce","cinemaId":"d516a0dd-b0ab-4e15-85b2-0286eaf6dde6","timeFrom":"2026-06-10T18:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-10T20:56:00+02:00","saleTimeTo":"2026-06-10T18:30:00+02:00","reservationTimeTo":"2026-06-10T17:00:00+02:00","availabilityStatus":1,"maxOccupancy":347,"audience":114,"generalAdmission":false,"isScreenSwapping":false,"externalId":835356,"items":[{"movieId":"efba3b90-d2db-4d41-b474-60d596a59302","moviePrintId":"4a18ef08-42c9-481a-b3ba-e757ea39fec5","timeFrom":"2026-06-10T18:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-10T20:56:00+02:00","movieName":"Drugie życie","speakingType":"Napisy","printType":"2D","screenId":"6f42a3dc-bbd0-4b84-897a-3d9badde17ce","movieSubPrintLabel":"PS"}],"tagGroups":[{"symbol":"Projekty Specjalne","description":"","tags":[{"orderNo":2,"symbol":"KINO KOBIET","description":""}]}],"restrictedToCardTypeIds":[],"screenFeatures":[]}]